title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E84 - Loose Ends
description: Brian Wayne Foster is joined by Travis Willingham, Liam O'Brien, Matthew Mercer, and Sam Riegel, for Talks Machina! They discuss Critical Role Episode #84, giving out fan art and gif of the week prizes, and answering questions!
